name: MOCTAIL VACCINE
description:
In my country, we got mixed vaccines!!!
Most people in my country got Sinovac and got the AstraZeneca as the booster!
Pfizer is not enough for all, it is for kids, doctors, and the elite!
We also need to pre-order for Moderna, pay on our own, and need to wait for 3-4 months!!!
The fake news about the situation is from the government too!!!!
We were locked down for a while without any compensation!!!!!
FUCK!
